{"tid":1404530,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"全部人同我入嚟幫手買嘢","createTime":"2019-08-04T04:59:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T09:42:14.000Z","uid":12264,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"081771e4dd70ee72312219afe36ddb9641c0b35f","tid":1404530,"uid":12264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T04:59:46.000Z","msg":"麻煩咁多位去佐敦嘅執笠倉支持下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我琴日發夢係屋企睇直播嘅時候<br />\n見到好多個幫手落閘嘅時候整壞左人哋個閘<br />\n換過一個全新嘅閘價錢都唔細<br />\n執笠倉呢間支持左我地好耐<br />\n加上琴日都有幾位勇士大力咁樣拉落嚟<br />\n搞到個閘成個彎晒<br />\n所以我覺得我哋應該負返小小責任<br />\n我今日都會去買嘢比下貼士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a9cc3e215ee8a0bd74e3d79076917f996f8433c","tid":1404530,"uid":152700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T05:03:49.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"5276e3c57d0ca246e201d672cc772100b06dbf9b","tid":1404530,"uid":12264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T05:07:04.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"4de173d175d045b204ea44f7ba4fca8ebe259fa8","tid":1404530,"uid":12264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T05:16:16.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"2198861caef968831f9e4de970922b10f63efee9","tid":1404530,"uid":12264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T05:33:10.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"3e1213cbf7653a1f35264943452d42843afd915d","tid":1404530,"uid":12264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T07:32:24.000Z","msg":"同我推撚爆佢"},{"pid":"8e9eecc55680e33676681c14fefd9f049a3987d4","tid":1404530,"uid":12264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T07:45:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92fa03d873a54f4cf0324e8ea1565a8e12048a2c","tid":1404530,"uid":12264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T07:57:02.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"bd8626b52765ea1b2c6f9863719d41dd553d3150","